<h1>Linked-List Mergesort</h1>

<p>
Very low tech visualization of bottom-up mergesort on a small linked list. This
follows the algorithm shown in Sedgewick, <span class="booktitle">Algorithms in
C++</span>, 1992 (pg.
170).
</p>

